{"tid":1609024,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[日經]黑警，對唔住，你地真係唔配做人","createTime":"2019-10-01T13:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T13:50:36.000Z","uid":297261,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc29795e32eba7ed22a5be94608997ff7e3b0f1a","tid":1609024,"uid":297261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:12:16.000Z","msg":"今日十一賀佢老母，當然熱烈恭喜十一國慶啦係咪先，賀佢老母臭閪。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就12點去發夢用上帝視覺去睇陣，轉左幾次場架啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當我發完夢攰攰地個陣，就收到有朋友send條片黎，見到有手足發夢個陣中槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個一下我直頭呆撚左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都識朋友做紀律部隊，佢地話開槍有一定守則要跟，有「一加一武力」，即係話要攻擊者用刀/致命武力，先可以拔槍，開槍前仲要警告。<br />\n睇番條片係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>完撚全無</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我望撚住個後生仔比人槍斃咁撚樣呀屌你老母</strong></span><br />\n當下成個人hang撚左機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />17歲，中五咋屌你老母。<br />\n係一個乜撚野政權要逼到個後生仔上黎抗爭呀！屌你老母！！！！！！<br />\nForce一日唔交人，政府一日唔成立獨立調查、唔落實雙普選，只會令抗爭持續，民憤越高！<br />\n就無論結果係點，你班仆街黑警一定會被清算！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家答應我，唔好原諒黑警好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n朋友要我幫手講埋：知唔知點解咁多紀律部隊高層都要企出黎撐警？因為班細既7，8成都黃到仆街，軍心一早散哂，popo眾叛親離，唯有靠班大佬將自己個部門綁落黑警到。<br />\n所以你見點解過關咁多料爆，唔好話FSD,海關入境都好多手足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點都好，天佑手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d19c5c17cc9383980a3cf5c2e7915424a12a69","tid":1609024,"uid":297261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"手足加油 全香港人都幫你打氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984e8099695a1781d2333ced63519af44eb2b72d","tid":1609024,"uid":297261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:15:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492ced7c71717cb771799fc709dc2e81f8ca4c57","tid":1609024,"uid":297261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:17:24.000Z","msg":"朋友話：<br />\n其實popo真係已經無哂朋友咁濟，如果大家想組隊打波，或者召喚魔法獸，相信好多人都會一呼百應。"},{"pid":"b9a035fe230754325dfba8b02106c35d87604cde","tid":1609024,"uid":297261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:17:46.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9998fd30e9ef68abfb01e462ade8adf31a115a","tid":1609024,"uid":297261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"大家要幫手足打氣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfebe6e4d9947689dc48eecb1a205251075ee6ae","tid":1609024,"uid":297261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:19:30.000Z","msg":"大家唔好忘記呢一幕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vvhq6f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVvhq6f4.jpg&h=ca8757b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4a219ed9d0f4f9b4e020a91a05243c16c0057ba","tid":1609024,"uid":98681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:33:47.000Z","msg":"無人會原諒佢地<br />\n原諒佢地嘅人都會被大家憎恨的"},{"pid":"5cbabaaa754b908383603f8dd411b90e4420254f","tid":1609024,"uid":268930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc29795e32eba7ed22a5be94608997ff7e3b0f1a","tid":1609024,"uid":297261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:12:16.000Z","msg":"今日十一賀佢老母，當然熱烈恭喜十一國慶啦係咪先，賀佢老母臭閪。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br